  <entry>
    <title>Linux环境搭建二：JDK安装教程</title>
    <link href="https://flowerunbeaten.github.io/post/47ad.html"/>
    <id>https://flowerunbeaten.github.io/post/47ad.html</id>
    <published>2022-11-10T02:45:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-11-14T01:38:52.732Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="卸载已有的OPEN-JDK"><a href="#卸载已有的OPEN-JDK" class="headerlink" title="卸载已有的OPEN JDK"></a>卸载已有的OPEN JDK</h3><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 输入以下命令检查是否存在<span class="keyword">open</span> jdk</span><br><span class="line">rpm -<span class="keyword">qa</span> | <span class="keyword">grep</span> java</span><br><span class="line"># 如果存在，则删除</span><br><span class="line">yum -<span class="keyword">y</span> <span class="built_in">remove</span> 对应<span class="keyword">open</span> jdk的名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span><h3 id="下载JDK"><a href="#下载JDK" class="headerlink" title="下载JDK"></a>下载JDK</h3><p><a href="https://www.oracle.com/">Oracle官网地址</a></p><p>我这里选择的版本是<a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase/javase8u211-later-archive-downloads.html#license-lightbox">jdk-8u341-linux-x64.tar.gz</a>，如果要选择其他版本可自行选择下载。</p><p>下载完成后，使用fxtp工具将下载的压缩文件上传至你服务器指定的文件夹下，我这里是&#x2F;home&#x2F;software。</p><h3 id="安装JDK"><a href="#安装JDK" class="headerlink" title="安装JDK"></a>安装JDK</h3><p>1、在&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;下创建java文件夹并进入。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/local/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> java</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> java</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2、将上面准备好的JDK安装包解压到&#x2F;usr&#x2F;lcoal&#x2F;java 文件夹下。</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf <span class="regexp">/home/</span>software<span class="regexp">/jdk-8u341-linux-x64.tar.gz -C ./</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>解压完成后，&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;java的文件夹下会出现一个jdk1.8.0_341的目录。</p><h3 id="配置JDK环境变量"><a href="#配置JDK环境变量" class="headerlink" title="配置JDK环境变量"></a>配置JDK环境变量</h3><p>编辑&#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile文件</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim <span class="regexp">/etc/</span>profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在文件的末尾加入如下配置。</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Java环境变量设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">JAVA_HOME</span>=/usr/local/java/jdk1.8.0_341</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">CLASSPATH</span>=<span class="variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">PATH</span>=<span class="variable">$PATH</span>:$JAVA_HOME/bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> PATH JAVA_HOME CLASSPATH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存并退出（ESC+:wq）</p><p>使配置文件生效</p><figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">source</span> <span class="regexp">/etc/</span>profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="验证JDK安装结果"><a href="#验证JDK安装结果" class="headerlink" title="验证JDK安装结果"></a>验证JDK安装结果</h3><p>依次输入下面的命令。</p><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">java</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword"></span><span class="keyword">javac</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword"></span><span class="keyword">java </span>-version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现下面的界面代表安装成功。</p><p><img src="https://flowerunbeaten-blog-images.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/images/202211102019581.png" alt="image-20221110201901523"></p><p><img src="https://flowerunbeaten-blog-images.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/images/202211102019656.png" alt="image-20221110201959596"></p><p><img src="https://flowerunbeaten-blog-images.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/images/202211102020551.png" alt="image-20221110202018519"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;卸载已有的OPEN-JDK&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#卸载已有的OPEN-JDK&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;卸载已有的OPEN JDK&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;卸载已有的OPEN JDK&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight vim&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 输入以下命令检查是否存在&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;open&lt;/span&gt; jdk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;rpm -&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;qa&lt;/span&gt; | &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;grep&lt;/span&gt; java&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 如果存在，则删除&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;yum -&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;y&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;remove&lt;/span&gt; 对应&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;open&lt;/span&gt; jdk的名称&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
